result.name: Katong Laksa Prawn Mee

reviews.text:
You come here for the Laksa, nothing else really. They serve a close replicate, authentic Laksa from Singapore, best thing is you can order Blood Cockles (Sea Harm) to go with your Laksa.

The tastes, flavor is spot on and the prices are fair and reasonable as well. This is as good as Singaporean hawker fare without having the need to physically be in Singapore.
This place has one of the most authentic Malaysian Singaporean dishes. It’s a very small outlet but the food and the aroma is astounding !

Weak laksa, terrible service. Laksa was quite weak and not particular flavoursome. Not a lot of heat. Also, they seem to be using wheat noodles, possibly spaghetti. The beef brisket was seriously tough and chewy. Service was with few words and emotionless, absolutely no smiles. That could be forgive if the food was good but unfortunately, this was not the case and I will not return.
You have to load up on the chillies to make it a 3 star. And it would have been a 4 star if the chilies were supplied on each table
First time trying laksa. I think they made it well here. Spicy, piping hot coconut noodle soup. I had 5c. Service was not the greatest, but it is a basic place.

reviews.text: A little pricy but taste good for a quick menu

Tried bakuteh. The soup is just too much of red dates flavour hence too sweet No danggui flavour at all. Meat just too dry and tough. 
Staff were OK, they were willing to provide extra minced garlic when I asked for it. Hkd 85 is quite pricey.
Very nice perfect taste spicy
So-so

hainan chicken takeaway: chicken was over cooked and tasted very dry.. the rice was cooked with too much water and the texture wasn’t pleasant. guess ordering chicken rice at a noodle place was my fault

result.name: 加東叻沙 蝦麵

reviews.text: 十個人十種口味，甜酸苦辣鹹體會人人有別，唯有相同的是馬來亞的味道，然而是否個個懂得又不得而知，用自家味蕾經歷來評價食品好壞其實意義不大。要了一碗正宗蝦麵，喝下了第一啖湯，味覺運作，和旅伴同遊馬拉的片段開始重播，超越了食事的二維度，整件事情是令人享受的。不過，過程需要代價。
A little pricy but taste good for a quick menu
好味，價錢合理
非常美味的 喇沙 最愛吃牛舌喇沙
朋友帶著我去吃星馬菜，今天再嚐喇沙，和昨天印象猶新的喇沙比較，今天的湯較稠膩、濃味，但昨天的更清鮮、芬香和吃得更舒服。蝦是昨天的更新鮮。兩者價錢也差不了太多，明顯是昨天的喇沙好太多了。另外點了肉骨茶，偏甜，支竹還未煮透，比起北角的肉骨茶店差太遠了。
